						<li class="mt-3">Requires a minimum of 74KiB RAM to execute a single WebAssembly program.</li>
						<li class="mt-3">Execution may be interrupted, and number of instructions executed may be tracked.</li>
						<li class="mt-3">Support for Windows, Mac, Linux, Android, iOS, and several other operating systems.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
